provisions for the establishment of an official 
planning commission. And in addition to that, the

30:45.678 --> 31:04.519
leaders, the economic leaders, the political 
leaders, and a great many of the citizens were able

30:45.678 --> 31:04.519
to come together and unite in

31:05.832 --> 31:13.939
preparing a comprehensive plan for the city.

